ss=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > However, a savage plague ravaging the land derails your plans.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alongside your bond mates and chosen allies, can you save the Elven Realm from destruction and take a step closer to your ultimate goal?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2580130/extras/4ed849648903eb9bc7479cbbfaeb7793.poster.avif?t=1770041850\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2580130/extras/4ed849648903eb9bc7479cbbfaeb7793.webm?t=1770041850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2580130/extras/4ed849648903eb9bc7479cbbfaeb7793.mp4?t=1770041850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow close to two new allies:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Morwen</strong> - a noble Moon Elf</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Idril </strong>- a Sun Elf Commander</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2580130/extras/f3171d9520bbfe63d7435cdc1fc417e8.poster.avif?t=1770041850\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2580130/extras/f3171d9520bbfe63d7435cdc1fc417e8.webm?t=1770041850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2580130/extras/f3171d9520bbfe63d7435cdc1fc417e8.mp4?t=1770041850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can explore numerous characters' stories in optional side content alongside the main story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to know them deeper and engage in more &quot;romantic encounters&quot;.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2580130/extras/9b14a44947ad6c85bda77a4115843343.poster.avif?t=1770041850\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2580130/extras/9b14a44947ad6c85bda77a4115843343.webm?t=1770041850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2580130/extras/9b14a44947ad6c85bda77a4115843343.mp4?t=1770041850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who did you choose as your allies? How do others view you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Continue your story by importing your choices from The Seven Realms: Terran &amp; Pythonium.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or start a brand new journey here with an immersive recap and save simulation, allowing you to jump straight into the Elven Realm. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2580130/extras/819c1bec18e8835f8c8cad62ba5459d6.poster.avif?t=1770041850\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2580130/extras/819c1bec18e8835f8c8cad62ba5459d6.webm?t=1770041850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2580130/extras/819c1bec18e8835f8c8cad62ba5459d6.mp4?t=1770041850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your choices will influence the future of the realms and impact those you love.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What kind of partner, ally and ruler wi